#Here, the main deck will be displayed. Clicking on the deck draws a card into your hand. Clicking on a card activates that card.

[?
if year == 1918 and month == 12 : An Electoral Commttee has been formed, Its members included: the National Democratic Party, the Christian Democratic Party, the Polish Progressive Party, the National Union, and the National Suffrage Action of Polish Women.<br><br>
After a few weeks, the following also joined: the Real Politics Party, the National Rebirth Party, the National Labor Party, the Political Circle of Workers' Associations, the Association of Christian Workers and the Economic Independence Union.<br><br>
Additionally a far left party has been formed,<span style="color: #890000;">**The Communist Workers' Party of Poland</span> was formed after the following the merger of the <span style="color: #855000;">Social Democracy of the Kingdom of Poland and Lithuania (SDKPiL)</span><br><br>
and <span style="color: #D03030;">PPS-Left</span>, the <span style="color: #890000;">Communist Workers' Party of Poland (KPRP)</span> has been formally established. Additionally Party has decided to Boycott the January Elections.
?]

- @party
- @govt
- #advisor
- @shuffle_leadership_pinned


